inter eNb handover as well as the mobility between LTE network and other 3GPP

networks. It also performs replication of the user trac in case of lawful interception.

- Packet-data Network Gateway P-GW: It connects the UE to the external net-
works by being the point of exit and entry of trac for the UE. It acts as the anchor for mobility between 3GPP and non-3GPP technologies such as WiMAX and 3GPP2 like CDMA 1X and EvDO.

